{"tid":1889604,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（絲入）大家試過點減肥最後係成功？","createTime":"2020-02-20T16:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T01:30:34.000Z","uid":341922,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"64c7352b0b040db47ea70718d4a374a7468b04da","tid":1889604,"uid":341922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"唉 減肥應該係我終身事業 呢世都脫離唔到<br />\n曾經成功瘦左d 宜家無留神又肥番<br />\n試過好多唔同方法 <br />\n包括搵PT 嚴格飲食控制 跑步 打拳 間歇性斷食 減肥藥 跳舞 西柚減肥&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我知減肥一定係要改變生活習慣先可以持之以恆<br />\n但我無用 意志唔夠堅定 又容易俾食物引誘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人一唔開心就亂咁食<br />\n<br />\n最近朋友推介蔬果汁斷食法<br />\n咁樣一定瘦 而且瘦得快<br />\n但個身形唔會好睇 同埋好易瘦埋個胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問問大家試過點樣減肥最後好成功？"},{"pid":"b7df097d795beef0b189a9e1647768292fda35d8","tid":1889604,"uid":280984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:02:18.000Z","msg":"我反而係唔開心就食唔落野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前同男朋友發生左d事 個半年係差唔多日日都唔開心 然後食少左野同無咩食零食就減到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c6a2032a01debd57c22f24de900f8fe32f6e63","tid":1889604,"uid":221635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"戒糖"},{"pid":"7697a9c93adfb0aa6e8279420446b6ba771847b9","tid":1889604,"uid":46752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:05:25.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;個人一唔開心就亂咁食&rdquo;<br />\n要搵健康版代替<br />\n不過有d菜式可能好難搵健康版代替，真係要自己煮先做到<br />\n一係就幫襯d勁貴嘅健康餐<br />\n其實搞間減肥餐廳應該好多人幫襯？咁耐都未人有搞"},{"pid":"ee4341d25493c3c6b9948e5a39eccd509294a781","tid":1889604,"uid":179863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"唔好亂咁斷食/食好少嘢/淨係食同一種食物減肥啦<br />\n唔健康既減肥方法減走既都只係肌肉同水份<br />\n搞到新陳代謝慢咗 脂肪又仲喺度<br />\n變返正常飲食又肥返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 有做運動減 但衰在食得多立雜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abde3e6e6682eeee00c5672e3366c4c43937ea8","tid":1889604,"uid":317984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:14:08.000Z","msg":"講咩都冇用最緊要持之以恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係嘅話一世肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d17e77d8bfc03e56d8fcc3a732a34dbc8b4174","tid":1889604,"uid":119017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:15:07.000Z","msg":"戒澱粉質同糖，瘦得好快"},{"pid":"8c571985c49b19a1c155298e834bd52655dde6dd","tid":1889604,"uid":341922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7df097d795beef0b189a9e1647768292fda35d8","tid":1889604,"uid":280984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:02:18.000Z","msg":"我反而係唔開心就食唔落野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前同男朋友發生左d事 個半年係差唔多日日都唔開心 然後食少左野同無咩食零食就減到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:17:52.000Z","msg":"個人唔開心 瘦左都無用<br />\n宜家解決左未啊？"},{"pid":"616fc34a0cb0255cee2b640948deec682c5d2900","tid":1889604,"uid":341922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51c6a2032a01debd57c22f24de900f8fe32f6e63","tid":1889604,"uid":221635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"戒糖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:18:29.000Z","msg":"就係去日本時日日食甜品累事<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a8404ac4d203005ee348a37c5ed897ec491a13","tid":1889604,"uid":341922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7697a9c93adfb0aa6e8279420446b6ba771847b9","tid":1889604,"uid":46752,"like":